{"tid":540024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國成功複製出靈長類，取名「中中」「華華」","createTime":"2018-01-25T06:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T00:06:09.000Z","uid":66943,"like":21,"dislike":108,"uniUserReply":108,"replies":[{"pid":"e657380695e2c3796ad4af7140b0c9301bb8271f","tid":540024,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:05:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image2.thenewslens.com/2018/1/qbr6bdc5ny4wvmtqjo5nvok99nu2av.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.thenewslens.com%2F2018%2F1%2Fqbr6bdc5ny4wvmtqjo5nvok99nu2av.jpg&h=d2e70c69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/88375\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F88375&d=0o5azslwCYS4FXC%2BZHkPgpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=df052e8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/88375</a><br />\n<br />\n國際學術期刊「細胞」（Cell）官網今（25）日凌晨發表了中國科學家的一項重大突破，他們已成功培育出體細胞核移植（SCNT）的複製猴，這是全球首例體細胞核移植複製猴。<br />\n<br />\n新華社報道，世上首隻複製猴「中中」於2017年11月27日誕生，10天後（同年12月5日）另一隻複製猴「華華」來到世上。學術期刊《細胞》於1月25日發布這項研究成果。<br />\n<br />\n中國突破複製靈長類動物屏障：複製猴「中中」「華華」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 為腦疾病研究帶來新希望<br />\nCloning of Macaque Monkeys by Somatic Cell Nuclear Transfer（Cell）<br />\n繼世上第一隻複製羊「桃莉（Dolly）」在1996年誕生後，21年來，各地科學家先後複製了牛，鼠，貓，狗等動物，但技術上一直沒有跨越與人類最相近的非人靈長類動物的屏障。<br />\n<br />\n2000年，科學家曾成功複製靈長類動物。當時美國俄勒岡國家靈長類動物研究中心成功誕生全球首隻非人靈長類的複製猴（Tetra），不過是採取胚胎分裂的方式。2010年，美國俄勒崗靈長類研究中心著名科學家米塔利波夫的團隊，成功移植了複製猴的胚胎，但胚胎发育至81天流產。這次「中中」、「華華」出現前，最接近成功的一次研究。<br />\n<br />\n中國科學院神經科學研究所研究員孫強率領的團隊攻克的是「體細胞核轉移（SCNT）」的難題，這種複製方法與知名的複製羊桃莉（Dolly）的方法類似。"},{"pid":"c7ad01f21fde7fde91d568497bf3b80d06debc86","tid":540024,"uid":61492,"like":156,"dislike":7,"score":149,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:06:30.000Z","msg":"兩隻馬嬲個樣笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個表情好驚訝"},{"pid":"4fb97e82618e02f11c1ed070796575bd4433f7e6","tid":540024,"uid":35746,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:07:07.000Z","msg":"教佢講英文"},{"pid":"ebd85e98fbbe5086921dc0cf51ffb6b0a53e09f3","tid":540024,"uid":101571,"like":4,"dislike":78,"score":-74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:08:29.000Z","msg":"複製出黎嘅有無思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個思想係咪同複製嘅一樣"},{"pid":"79aae17dcac38957f5a26a69fc91cc3ec1305cff","tid":540024,"uid":83328,"like":297,"dislike":4,"score":293,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:08:38.000Z","msg":"過幾日釘左就多得佢唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天滅中華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36e92f89b1a7b41d77294852fdac66be5f04421","tid":540024,"uid":102765,"like":148,"dislike":8,"score":140,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:08:41.000Z","msg":"點解唔叫支支同那那"},{"pid":"0e9b68565c7c5c1b17a01b48622ec88924389a12","tid":540024,"uid":900,"like":112,"dislike":4,"score":108,"quote":{"pid":"c7ad01f21fde7fde91d568497bf3b80d06debc86","tid":540024,"uid":61492,"like":156,"dislike":7,"score":149,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:06:30.000Z","msg":"兩隻馬嬲個樣笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個表情好驚訝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:10:32.000Z","msg":"好似扑野比人撞破咁既表情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82040c12a86793d86846d978318a48b4faf5e40e","tid":540024,"uid":130105,"like":133,"dislike":3,"score":130,"quote":{"pid":"c7ad01f21fde7fde91d568497bf3b80d06debc86","tid":540024,"uid":61492,"like":156,"dislike":7,"score":149,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:06:30.000Z","msg":"兩隻馬嬲個樣笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個表情好驚訝"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:12:17.000Z","msg":"一出世做咗中國人<i